### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### POST /members — cas normal (201) ✅
### Parrains 1 & 2 sont dans la collectivité 1 et ont > 90 jours d'ancienneté
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST http://localhost:8080/members
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "firstName": "Tahiry",
    "lastName": "Andriamanana",
    "birthDate": "1998-03-15",
    "gender": "MALE",
    "address": "Lot 22 Ankadivato Antananarivo",
    "profession": "Agriculteur",
    "phoneNumber": "0341000020",
    "email": "tahiry.andria@email.com",
    "occupation": "JUNIOR",
    "collectivityIdentifier": 1,
    "referees": [1, 2],
    "registrationFeePaid": true,
    "membershipDuesPaid": true
  }
]

